verbose_text: Although the exact pathogenesis is still debatable, a complex interaction between genetic and environmental factors triggers an up-regulation of T helper 1 (Th1) and 17 (Th17) pathways, giving rise to increased levels of tumour necrosis factor (TNF) and IL-17/22 [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
